DROP - Put down an item
=======================

Usage: drop <item>

Drops an item from your inventory onto the ground.

Examples:
  drop sword
  drop tooth

Notes:
  - You cannot drop a wielded weapon (use 'unwield' first)
  - You cannot drop worn armor (use 'remove' first)
  - Dropped items stay in the room until picked up

See also: help get, help inventory, help unwield, help remove
